{"tid":775092,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"麻煩 許彤 小姐 入一入黎","createTime":"2018-08-11T00:46:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-28T17:56:21.000Z","uid":10277,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"610412f3d8525a755e6fe6bea225264642b75636","tid":775092,"uid":10277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T00:46:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/11/082217_f1beaf76354aee7979d9f14e2d7860cb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F11%2F082217_f1beaf76354aee7979d9f14e2d7860cb.png&h=720ecc90&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 肥菜先生 的確係一個網絡好知名嘅網絡9upper<br />\n<br />\n老實講我都有follow你同埋肥菜<br />\n佢大部分post都係優質過你好多 <br />\n<br />\n雖然佢hate大陸人、南亞人、閪女人<br />\n（唔知係咪你所指嘅一次過hate好多人）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你自己都hate話你做雞又樣衰嘅人<br />\n<br />\n肥菜嘅post會令人唔開心嘅時候都可以開心返 <br />\n就算係社會問題佢都用一個好搞笑嘅方式去講<br />\n而你嘅post 有時候直接講好多你認同嘅道理<br />\n打一堆字講自己感受 盲嘅都知邊個容易入屋d<br />\n<br />\n無論係名氣、內涵，<br />\n肥菜＞＞＞許彤<br />\n<br />\n你有無上過報紙頭版同TVB新聞呀？<br />\n點計都係你先係hater喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc126d027fab8f8f453055063190ceffa90308cc","tid":775092,"uid":187729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T01:37:21.000Z","msg":"見到樓主咁認真對待啲花邊嘢，第一下就心諗條友係咪弱智<br />\n<br />\n睇下d舊po，原來真係弱智"},{"pid":"2d121522c5a1a38ee5baf1593540501f89b934db","tid":775092,"uid":60959,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T14:10:43.000Z","msg":"哇屌有人吹奏我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75a875d5423c4873d6bc702968dba17d12265940","tid":775092,"uid":10277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2d121522c5a1a38ee5baf1593540501f89b934db","tid":775092,"uid":60959,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T14:10:43.000Z","msg":"哇屌有人吹